<paragraph blockId="14.[151,1437,608,2001]" pageId="14" pageNumber="81">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,265,608,633]" pageId="14" pageNumber="81">
<typeStatus box="[151,261,608,633]" pageId="14" pageNumber="81">Syntypes</typeStatus>
.
</emphasis>
Male, 
<collectionCode box="[344,428,609,632]" pageId="14" pageNumber="81">BMNH</collectionCode>
<number box="[436,515,608,633]" pageId="14" pageNumber="81" value="1946.8">1946.8</number>
. 
<number box="[518,585,608,633]" pageId="14" pageNumber="81" value="27.39">27.39</number>
, SVL 
<quantity box="[657,760,608,633]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="6.76" pageId="14" pageNumber="81" unit="mm" value="67.6">67.6 mm</quantity>
, 
<collectingCountry box="[772,832,608,633]" name="India" pageId="14" pageNumber="81">India</collectingCountry>
, presented by J. E. Gray; male, 
<collectionCode box="[1190,1274,609,632]" pageId="14" pageNumber="81">BMNH</collectionCode>
<number box="[1282,1361,608,633]" pageId="14" pageNumber="81" value="1946.8">1946.8</number>
. 
<number box="[1365,1432,608,633]" pageId="14" pageNumber="81" value="27.4">27.40</number>
, SVL 60.0 mm, 
<collectingCountry box="[336,396,644,669]" name="India" pageId="14" pageNumber="81">India</collectingCountry>
, presented by J. E. Gray. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[704,767,644,669]" pageId="14" pageNumber="81">Note.</emphasis>
We discovered the original 
<typeStatus box="[1101,1149,645,669]" pageId="14" pageNumber="81">type</typeStatus>
series of 
<taxonomicName box="[1269,1435,644,669]" class="Reptilia" family="Agamidae" genus="Sitana" kingdom="Animalia" order="Squamata" pageId="14" pageNumber="81" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="deccanensis">
<emphasis box="[1269,1435,644,669]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="81">S. deccanensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(comprising two 
<typeStatus box="[346,446,680,704]" pageId="14" pageNumber="81">syntypes</typeStatus>
) among the 
<typeStatus box="[592,690,681,705]" pageId="14" pageNumber="81">syntypes</typeStatus>
of 
<taxonomicName authority="Gunther, 1864" authorityName="Gunther" authorityYear="1864" box="[731,1000,680,705]" class="Reptilia" family="Agamidae" genus="Sitana" kingdom="Animalia" order="Squamata" pageId="14" pageNumber="81" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="minor">
<emphasis box="[731,828,681,704]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="81">S. minor</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Gunther" box="[837,1000,680,705]" pageId="14" pageNumber="81" refString="Gunther, A. C. L. G. (1864) The Reptiles of British India. The Ray Society, London, 452 pp." type="book" year="1864">
Günther, 
<number box="[944,1000,680,705]" pageId="14" pageNumber="81" value="1864.0">1864</number>
</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
and they probably got mixed up later (probably after 
<number box="[325,385,717,741]" pageId="14" pageNumber="81" value="1870.0">1870</number>
).
</paragraph>
